<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天就是等了又等的烟花大会举办的日子了！<10_4 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />晚上7点<tag a="110" b="0" />这座<tag a="110" b="32" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就会被魔法的光芒包裹。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实我从今天早上就开始忐忑不安。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你问为什么<tag a="110" b="0" />？<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那是因为今天晚上7点起有烟花大会！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我对你出席烟花大会的打扮<delay20 />
也很期待哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />你也会来的吧？<10_4 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚7点的烟花大会将带来一个怎样的夜晚，<delay20 />
太令人期待了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已经做好心理准备了吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="8" />的上空，<delay20 />
马上就会绽放出无数花朵了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花大会很令人期待吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在的心情<delay8 />就像是<delay20 />
在等待前来赴约的恋人一般<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如此一想，<delay20 />
像这样让我心焦的等待时间<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也没有那么难熬了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />马上就要到烟花大会开始的时间了啊。<10_4 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在此之前，要不要先去场地<delay20 />
仔细地探一探情况呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了能将最美的瞬间<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />映在心之相机的底片里……</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀～<delay20 />这次的烟花大会<delay20 />
实在是太妙了～<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要说这次烟花的美丽程度，<delay20 />
可能是我至今见识过的烟花中<delay20 />
排名数一数二的～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来，不仅烟花令人赞不绝口，<delay20 />
大家欢快的表情也令我印象深刻。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次举办活动，<tag a="110" b="32" />上就活力十足，真好啊！</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抬头仰望烟花的时候，<delay frames="30" />
我禁不住深深感叹，<delay8 />
幸好有来<tag a="110" b="8" />。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已经<delay20 />完全中招了，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />被<tag a="110" b="8" />的魔法击中……</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />现在闭上双眼的话，<delay20 />
还能回想出今年最后的烟花大会<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望明年也可以有幸和大家一起欣赏。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的烟花大会也结束了啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />活动结束之后，<delay20 />
你会感到落寞吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过在感到落寞的同时，<delay20 />
我们的时间已经推进了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以此时此刻，<delay20 />
我们应该尽情想象接下来会发生的开心事。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比如说明年的烟花大会，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样的话就不会感到失落了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这次烟花大会<delay20 />
是今年的最后一场。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />无论参与什么样的活动，<delay20 />
每一次经历最后都能成为<delay20 />
不可替代的、弥足珍贵的回忆。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想在今后的日子里，<delay20 />
和<tag a="110" b="8" />的伙伴们一起<delay20 />
参加各种活动，传递欢声笑语～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>